Package: msci.com
Title: MSCI Index Data Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for MSCI index data. Fetches daily and
    monthly index levels, performance comparisons, and reference codes for
    major MSCI indexes. Includes LLM context injection via msci_context().
